Uh...

718
01:00:55,862 --> 01:00:58,626
Uh...

719
01:01:37,604 --> 01:01:39,868
Mother!

720
01:01:39,906 --> 01:01:43,398
What is it, dear? What's the matter?

721
01:01:44,911 --> 01:01:47,744
Oh!

722
01:01:53,319 --> 01:01:56,254
Al Malone, the deputy, just called.
He wants me over at the Fawcett place.

723
01:01:56,322 --> 01:01:58,415
Some detectives from
Santa Rosa will be there.

724
01:01:58,525 --> 01:02:02,154
- Will it be all right?
- Yes. I was just taking your mother
in some tea.

725
01:02:04,364 --> 01:02:07,060
Oh, be careful, please.

726
01:02:16,910 --> 01:02:18,878
And you be careful?

727
01:02:51,211 --> 01:02:55,147
Mitch?

728
01:02:55,248 --> 01:02:57,512
No, it's me, Mrs. Brenner.

729
01:02:57,550 --> 01:03:01,953
- I thought you might like some tea.
- Oh. Thank you.

730
01:03:03,790 --> 01:03:07,351
- Where's Mitch?
- Al Malone wanted him out
at the Fawcett farm.

731
01:03:07,460 --> 01:03:10,361
Why? Didn't Al believe my story?

732
01:03:10,463 --> 01:03:13,227
He was calling from the farm.

733
01:03:13,266 --> 01:03:16,064
Then he saw. Oh, he must have.

734
01:03:16,102 --> 01:03:18,400
They sent for the Santa Rosa police.

735
01:03:18,471 --> 01:03:21,907
What good will they do?

736
01:03:24,010 --> 01:03:25,910
Do you think Cathy's
all right at the school?

737
01:03:27,380 --> 01:03:30,611
Yes, I'm sure she's fine.

738
01:03:30,683 --> 01:03:34,585
Do I sound very foolish to you?

739
01:03:34,621 --> 01:03:36,589
Oh, no.

740
01:03:39,692 --> 01:03:41,990
I keep seeing Dan's face.

741
01:03:42,095 --> 01:03:44,393
And they have such
big windows at the school.

742
01:03:44,497 --> 01:03:46,431
All the windows are
broken in Dan's bedroom.

743
01:03:46,499 --> 01:03:50,333
- All the windows!
- Try not to think about that.

744
01:03:51,704 --> 01:03:54,696
I wish I were a stronger person.

745
01:03:59,112 --> 01:04:01,979
I lost my husband four years ago,
you know.

746
01:04:03,983 --> 01:04:05,746
It's terrible how you... you depend on

747
01:04:05,852 --> 01:04:07,547
someone else for strength, and then...

748
01:04:09,656 --> 01:04:12,784
