and you're alone.

749
01:04:18,298 --> 01:04:21,893
I'd love to be able to relax sometime.

750
01:04:22,001 --> 01:04:24,663
I'd love to be able to sleep.

751
01:04:27,173 --> 01:04:30,609
- Do you think Cathy's all right?
- Annie's there.

752
01:04:30,677 --> 01:04:33,407
